  "content": [
    {
      "id": "slide-intro",
      "type": "slide",
      "title": "简介",
      "description": "报告简介页",
      "layout": {
        "type": "title-content",
        "autoLayout": true
      },
      "components": [
        {
          "id": "text-intro",
          "type": "text",
          "dataProperties": {
            "dataType": "static",
            "title": "报告概述",
            "content": "本演示文稿用于测试PPT导出功能，包括：\n• 文本组件\n• 表格组件\n• 各类图表\n• 复合表组件"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "section-data",
      "type": "section",
      "title": "数据展示",
      "description": "表格和图表展示",
      "slides": [
        {
          "id": "slide-table",
          "type": "slide",
          "title": "数据表格",
          "layout": {
            "type": "content",
            "autoLayout": true
          },
          "components": [
            {
              "id": "table-ppt",
              "type": "table",
              "dataProperties": {
                "dataType": "static",
                "title": "季度业绩表",
                "columns": [
                  { "key": "quarter", "title": "季度", "type": "dimension" },
                  { "key": "revenue", "title": "营收(万)", "type": "measure" },
                  { "key": "growth", "title": "增长率", "type": "measure" }
                ],
                "data": [
                  { "quarter": "Q1", "revenue": 500, "growth": "15%" },
                  { "quarter": "Q2", "revenue": 620, "growth": "24%" },
                  { "quarter": "Q3", "revenue": 580, "growth": "-6%" },
                  { "quarter": "Q4", "revenue": 750, "growth": "29%" }
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "slide-charts",
          "type": "slide",
          "title": "图表展示",
          "layout": {
            "type": "two-column",
            "autoLayout": true
          },
          "components": [
            {
              "id": "chart-bar-ppt",
              "type": "chart",
              "dataProperties": {
                "dataType": "static",
                "title": "营收趋势",
                "columns": [
                  { "key": "quarter", "title": "季度", "type": "dimension" },
                  { "key": "revenue", "title": "营收", "type": "measure" }
                ],
                "data": [
                  { "quarter": "Q1", "revenue": 500 },
                  { "quarter": "Q2", "revenue": 620 },
                  { "quarter": "Q3", "revenue": 580 },
                  { "quarter": "Q4", "revenue": 750 }
                ],
                "series": [
                  { "type": "bar", "name": "营收", "encode": { "x": "quarter", "y": "revenue" } }
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "slide-markdown",
      "type": "slide",
      "title": "Markdown内容",
      "layout": {
        "type": "content",
        "autoLayout": true
      },
      "components": [
        {
          "id": "md-ppt",
          "type": "markdown",
          "dataProperties": {
            "dataType": "static",
            "content": "## 关键要点\n\n1. **第一季度**：稳步增长\n2. **第二季度**：加速扩张\n3. **第三季度**：短暂调整\n4. **第四季度**：强势反弹\n\n### 总结\n\n全年营收*2450万*，同比增长**18%**。"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "slide-composite",
      "type": "slide",
      "title": "复合表展示",
      "layout": {
        "type": "content",
        "autoLayout": true
      },
      "components": [
        {
          "id": "composite-ppt",
          "type": "compositeTable",
          "tables": [
            {
              "id": "sub-1",
              "type": "table",
              "dataProperties": {
                "dataType": "static",
                "title": "产品线A",
                "columns": [
                  { "key": "month", "title": "月份" },
                  { "key": "sales", "title": "销量" }
                ],
                "data": [
                  { "month": "1月", "sales": 100 },
                  { "month": "2月", "sales": 120 }
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "sub-2",
              "type": "table",
              "dataProperties": {
                "dataType": "static",
                "title": "产品线B",
                "columns": [
                  { "key": "month", "title": "月份" },
                  { "key": "sales", "title": "销量" }
                ],
                "data": [
                  { "month": "1月", "sales": 80 },
                  { "month": "2月", "sales": 95 }
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "dataProperties": {
            "dataType": "static",
            "title": "多产品线对比"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "summary": {
    "id": "ppt-summary",
    "overview": "本PPT完整展示了分页报告的所有组件类型，包括文本、Markdown、表格、图表和复合表。所有内容均已成功导出为PPT格式。"
  }
